name: Dataset
description: A body of structured information describing some topic(s) of interest.
title: Dataset

fields.name: includedInDataCatalog
fields.title: includedInDataCatalog
fields.description: A data catalog which contains this dataset.

fields.name: datasetTimeInterval
fields.title: datasetTimeInterval
fields.description: The range of temporal applicability of a dataset, e.g. for a 2011 census dataset, the year 2011 (in ISO 8601 time interval format).

fields.name: catalog
fields.title: catalog
fields.description: A data catalog which contains this dataset.

fields.name: issn
fields.title: issn
fields.description: The International Standard Serial Number (ISSN) that identifies this serial publication. You can repeat this property to identify different formats of, or the linking ISSN (ISSN-L) for, this serial publication.

fields.name: spatial
fields.title: spatial
fields.description: The range of spatial applicability of a dataset, e.g. for a dataset of New York weather, the state of New York.

fields.name: temporal
fields.title: temporal
fields.description: The range of temporal applicability of a dataset, e.g. for a 2011 census dataset, the year 2011 (in ISO 8601 time interval format).

fields.name: includedDataCatalog
fields.title: includedDataCatalog
fields.description: A data catalog which contains this dataset (this property was previously 'catalog', preferred name is now 'includedInDataCatalog').

fields.name: distribution
fields.title: distribution
fields.description: A downloadable form of this dataset, at a specific location, in a specific format.
